Package: ssnorms
Title: Calculates Norms for Sports Science Metrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "Amoako", , "mamoako@nd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package can calculate percentiles for a multitude of sports science metrics. The calcnorm function calculates 
  percentiles for entire teams while the idnorm function calculates percentiles for a specific individual.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
